 parties and presents!

50
00:03:45,079 --> 00:03:48,079
 So, Bridget, have you got your
 Christmas stocking ready?

51
00:03:48,640 --> 00:03:51,640
 She's taking her stockings off
 in the taxi!

52
00:03:53,959 --> 00:03:56,959
 Don't wait up.

53
