00:07:15,639 --> 00:07:18,639
 My sleigh! I forgot!

87
00:07:37,079 --> 00:07:39,158
 Mince pies!

88
00:07:39,159 --> 00:07:41,999
 First, the pastry!

89
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:45,000
 And now the minced meat
