 Delicious...Delicious.

102
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:08,360
 You know, Hector,
 Christmas is all about sharing.

103
00:09:11,279 --> 00:09:14,279
 Would you like some, Charley?

104
00:09:33,439 --> 00:09:36,439
 It's Saint Nicholas!

105
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:38,878
 What happened to your beard?

106
