00:12:18,159 --> 00:12:20,399
 Merrlly on high...

144
00:12:20,400 --> 00:12:23,159
 Get 'em, Gnasher!

145
00:12:23,160 --> 00:12:26,160
 Come all ye faithful

146
00:12:26,479 --> 00:12:29,479
 Joyful and tri...

